BAYVIEW LOAN SERVICING, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Juan GONZALEZ, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D16-0719 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017
